CS NORTHRIDGE SWEEPS BALL ST. 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In a meeting of nationally-ranked college volleyball teams, sixth-ranked Cal 
State Northridge swept ninth-ranked Ball State, 15-6, 15-9, 15-5, at Northridge 
on Monday. 
</P>
<P>
Raphael Tulino had a match-high 15 kills for Northridge (9-6), which hit .363 
as a team in the nonconference match. Coley Kyman and Neil Coffman added 10 and 
eight kills. 
</P>
