<P>
SAN DIEGO SPORTS ET CETERA: MEN'S BASKETBALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Christian Heritage meets Southern California College in the NAIA District 3 
championship game at 7:30 tonight at Whittier College. 
</P>
<P>
The Hawks (29-5), in only their fourth season of intercollegiate basketball, 
have won 11 consecutive games and 20 of their last 21. 
</P>
<P>
Southern California (24-8) defeated Westmont, 88-83, in overtime Saturday and 
the Hawks rallied to an 84-69 victory over Fresno Pacific to reach the final. 
</P>
<P>
The winner advances to the NAIA National Tournament beginning March 13 at 
Kansas City. 
</P>
