<P>
GATHERS, HANK; LOYOLA MARYMOUNT UNIVERSITY; BASKETBALL PLAYERS; SPORTS DEATHS; 
COLLEGE ATHLETICS; TELEVISION BROADCASTS; ETHICS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
