<P>
AMERICAN EXPRESS CO; BROKERAGE FIRMS; SECURITIES INDUSTRY -- LABOR RELATIONS; 
SECURITIES INDUSTRY -- LAYOFFS; BUSINESS CLOSINGS; SHEARSON LEHMAN HUTTON INC 
</P>
