<SUBJECT>
<P>
UNIONS; AMERICAN FEDERATION OF TEACHERS; NATIONAL EDUCATION ASSOCIATION; 
EDUCATION REFORM; UNITED STATES -- SCHOOLS; UNITED STATES -- EDUCATION; 
TEACHERS -- UNITED STATES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
