LOYOLA MARYMOUNT UNIVERSITY; BASKETBALL PLAYERS; DOCTORS; SPORTS DEATHS; 
PHYSICAL EXAMINATIONS; MEDICAL TREATMENTS; DIAGNOSTIC TESTS; MEDICINE 
</P>
